ated. Finally, we estimate how well the lensing bispectrum can constrain a\nmodel with primordial non-Gaussianity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Oct 2003 19:58:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 9 Dec 2003 15:37:19 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 14 Sep 2004 05:50:24 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 20 Jul 2005 13:41:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-04-06"}
