 transition. Analysis of the HCN and HNC 4-3\ntransitions provides further support for high densities n> 10^7 cm^-3 in all\nthe protostellar sources.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Oct 2003 22:10:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
